wiki.content: "Ada" is a track from The National album entitled Boxer, and features Sufjan Stevens on the piano. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
wiki.summary: "Ada" is a track from The National album entitled Boxer, and features Sufjan Stevens on the piano.
